<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hopeful-adj">hopeful <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'həʊpfl/    美 /'hoʊpfl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-optimistic">1.★ <strong>怀有希望的 (optimistic)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I became more <strong>hopeful about</strong> my future.
我对自己的未来更加充满希望。</p><footer>人教① – 2</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The fans are all <strong>hopeful (that)</strong> the team will do well this year.
球迷都希望球队今年能有良好的表现。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-promising">2.<strong>给人以希望的 (promising)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Only in this way will our society be more harmonious and hopeful.
只有这样我们的社会才会更加和谐、更加有希望。</p><footer>2012 湖南书面表达</footer></div></div>